text: KFLK-LP (95.9 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Minot, North Dakota. The station is owned by Calvary Chapel Minot and airs a religious format. The station was assigned the KFLK-LP call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on July 1, 2014. ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * FLK-LP FLK-LP Category:Radio stations established in 2015 Category:2015 establishments in North Dakota Category:Religious radio stations in the United States Category:Ward County, North Dakota FLK-LP
